The features and advantages of the process and the system will be more clearly understood from the following description taken in conjunction with the accompanying drawings in which:


FIGS. 1A to 1D are cross sectional views showing the prior art process disclosed in the Japanese Patent Publication of Unexamined Application;


FIGS. 2A to 2C are cross sectional views showing the prior art process disclosed in the Advanced Metallization for ULSI Applications;


FIG. 3 is a view showing the arrangement of a system for forming a thin film according to the present invention;


FIG. 4 is a cross sectional view showing a film forming apparatus incorporated in the system;


FIGS. 5A to 5D are cross sectional views showing a process sequence for forming a thin film according to the present invention;


FIG. 6 is a cross sectional view showing the structure of another film forming apparatus according to the present invention; and


FIGS. 7A to 7D are cross sectional views showing another process sequence for forming a thin film according to the present invention.

